- H2: 4 + 2 = 6 (on left), can reduce to C: 6
- O2: 2 (on left), can reduce to C: 2
- C: 8 (on right)
- Ve is also balanced.

- C: 8 (on left), can reduce to C: 8; and (on right) 6 + 2 = 8
